# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Missive → OneNote Integration — Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# These are set as Wrangler SECRETS (not in wrangler.toml) via:
#   wrangler secret put MICROSOFT_CLIENT_ID
#   wrangler secret put MICROSOFT_CLIENT_SECRET
#
# For local dev, create a file called .dev.vars (git-ignored) with:
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Azure App Registration → Overview
MICROSOFT_CLIENT_ID=xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx

# Azure App Registration → Certificates & Secrets → Client secret (value)
MICROSOFT_CLIENT_SECRET=your-client-secret-value-here
